| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1169 — Recovery Inhibition (BrainCipher)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e3fd2d73-c23f-5f13-ba37-f52a6ba8a415"
